public enum Result
extends Enum<Result>

Possible results of a submission to the Sphere Online Judge (SPOJ).

Author:
Miorel-Lucian Palii
See Also:
Sphere Online Judge (SPOJ)

Enum Constant Summary
AC
          Accepted: the submission was accepted by the judge.
CE
          Compilation Error: the submission was not executed because it did not compile.
PENDING
          Pending: the submission has not yet been judged.
RE
          Runtime Error: the submission crashed while running.
SE
          System Error: there was a system error while the submission was running.
TLE
          Time Limit Exceeded: the submission did not finish running in the allowed time.
WA
          Wrong Answer: the submission's output did not match the criteria expected by the judge.
